OL,3,CGove unveils new extremism definition
OL,4,Cto tackle 'challenge' to democracy
OL,6,FThe Government has unveiled its new
OL,7,Fdefinition of extremism amid rising
OL,8,Fconcern about threats to social
OL,9,Fcohesion and British democracy.
OL,11,FGroups covered by the definition,
OL,12,Fwhich is designed to include conduct
OL,13,Fthat falls short of criminality but is
OL,14,Fstill deemed "unacceptable", will be
OL,15,Fdenied access to Government funding
OL,16,Fand prevented from meeting ministers
OL,17,Fand officials or gaining a platform
OL,18,Fthat could "legitimise" them through
OL,19,Fassociation with the Government.
