OL,3,CGove unveils new extremism definition
OL,4,Cto tackle 'challenge' to democracy
OL,6,FThe definition describes extremism as
OL,7,F"the promotion or advancement of an
OL,8,Fideology based on violence, hatred or
OL,9,Fintolerance" that aims to "negate or
OL,10,Fdestroy the fundamental rights and
OL,11,Ffreedoms of others" or "undermine,
OL,12,Foverturn or replace the UK's system of
OL,13,Fliberal parliamentary democracy and
OL,14,Fdemocratic rights".
OL,16,FIt also includes those who
OL,17,F"intentionally create a permissive
OL,18,Fenvironment for others to achieve"
OL,19,Feither of those aims.
