OL,3,CGove unveils new extremism definition
OL,4,Cto tackle 'challenge' to democracy
OL,6,FThe previous definition, published in
OL,7,F2011, described extremism as "vocal or
OL,8,Factive opposition to fundamental
OL,9,FBritish values, including democracy,
OL,10,Fthe rule of law, individual liberty
OL,11,Fand mutual respect and tolerance of
OL,12,Fdifferent faiths and belief" as well
OL,13,Fas "calls for the death of members of
OL,14,Four armed forces".
