OL,3,CGove unveils new extremism definition
OL,4,Cto tackle 'challenge' to democracy
OL,6,FCommunities Secretary Michael Gove,
OL,7,Fwho has overseen the formulation of
OL,8,Fthe new definition, said the new
OL,9,Fdefinition would "ensure that
OL,10,FGovernment does not inadvertently
OL,11,Fprovide a platform to those setting
OL,12,Fout to subvert democracy and deny
OL,13,Fother people's fundamental rights".
OL,15,FHe added that it was the first in "a
OL,16,Fseries of measures to tackle extremism
OL,17,Fand protect our democracy".
