OL,3,CGove unveils new extremism definition
OL,4,Cto tackle 'challenge' to democracy
OL,6,FThe new definition comes into force on
OL,7,FThursday, and the Government is
OL,8,Fexpected to publish a list of
OL,9,Forganisations covered by it in the
OL,10,Fcoming weeks.
OL,12,FGroups on the list will only be able
OL,13,Fto appeal against their inclusion by
OL,14,Flaunching a judicial review in the
OL,15,FHigh Court.
OL,17,FLabour said the new definition was
OL,18,F"not enough" and called for a full
OL,19,Fcounter-extremism strategy and hate
OL,20,Fcrime action plan to "turn words into
OL,21,Faction that will keep us safe".
