OL,6,FAngela Rayner, the party's deputy
OL,7,Fleader and shadow communities
OL,8,Fsecretary, said: "Hateful extremism
OL,9,Fthreatens the safety of our
OL,10,Fcommunities and the unity of our
OL,11,Fcountry ` there is no place for it in
OL,12,FBritain.
OL,14,F"Labour is steadfast in our commitment
OL,15,Fto work across communities to ensure
OL,16,Fno one feels unsafe at the hands of
OL,17,Fcorrosive extremism.
