OL,3,CGove unveils new extremism definition
OL,4,Cto tackle 'challenge' to democracy
OL,6,F"This is a serious problem that needs
OL,7,Fserious action and tinkering with a
OL,8,Fnew definition is not enough. The
OL,9,FGovernment's counter-extremism
OL,10,Fstrategy is now nine years out of
OL,11,Fdate, and they've repeatedly failed to
OL,12,Fdefine Islamophobia.
OL,14,F"Any suggestion that the Government
OL,15,Fhas been engaging with groups that
OL,16,Fthey've now decided are extremists
OL,17,Fraises serious questions over why it
OL,18,Fhas taken so long to act."
