OL,3,CGove unveils new extremism definition
OL,4,Cto tackle 'challenge' to democracy
OL,6,FThe overhaul of the definition follows
OL,7,FRishi Sunak's impromptu speech in
OL,8,FDowning Street on March 1 in which he
OL,9,Fwarned of "forces here at home trying
OL,10,Fto tear us apart", although work on
OL,11,Fthe definition has been ongoing for a
OL,12,Fnumber of months.
OL,14,FBut the prospect of redefining
OL,15,Fextremism has also raised concerns
OL,16,Fthat too broad a definition could
OL,17,Fthreaten freedom of speech, worship
OL,18,Fand protest.
