OL,3,CGove unveils new extremism definition
OL,4,Cto tackle 'challenge' to democracy
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, the Archbishops of
OL,7,FCanterbury and York issued a warning
OL,8,Fthat the definition could "vilify the
OL,9,Fwrong people and risk yet more
OL,10,Fdivision" instead of "providing
OL,11,Fclarity or striking a conciliatory
OL,12,Ftone".
OL,14,FBut the Government has been keen to
OL,15,Fstress that it is a narrower
OL,16,Fdefinition than the 2011 Prevent
OL,17,Fversion, and provides a "high bar"
OL,18,Fthat "only captures the most
OL,19,Fconcerning of activities" and is "not
OL,20,Fabout silencing those with private and
OL,21,Fpeaceful beliefs".
