OL,3,CGove unveils new extremism definition
OL,4,Cto tackle 'challenge' to democracy
OL,6,FMr Gove said: "The United Kingdom is a
OL,7,Fsuccess story ` a multi-national,
OL,8,Fmulti-ethnic, multi-faith democracy.
OL,9,FIt is stronger because of its
OL,10,Fdiversity.
OL,12,F"But our democracy and our values of
OL,13,Finclusivity and tolerance are under
OL,14,Fchallenge from extremists. In order to
OL,15,Fprotect our democratic values, it is
OL,16,Fimportant both to reinforce what we
OL,17,Fhave in common and to be clear and
OL,18,Fprecise in identifying the dangers
OL,19,Fposed by extremism."
