OL,6,FLord Walney, the Government's adviser
OL,7,Fon political violence and disruption,
OL,8,Fwelcomed the new definition, saying:
OL,9,F"Greater clarity in defining extremism
OL,10,Fcan underpin a concerted approach
OL,11,Facross civil society to protect our
OL,12,Fcountry."
OL,14,FBut Conservative peer Baroness Warsi
OL,15,Fcriticised the move, calling it a
OL,16,F"divide and rule approach" intended to
OL,17,F"breed division and encourage
OL,18,Fmistrust".
