OL,6,F"Extremism is a grave concern, and we
OL,7,Fall stand in opposition to it, despite
OL,8,Fthe efforts of bigots to suggest
OL,9,Fotherwise through baseless
OL,10,Faccusations."
OL,12,FShe added: "With elections looming,
OL,13,Fit's unsurprising that the Government
OL,14,Fis resorting to this desperate tactic
OL,15,Fin the culture war."
OL,17,FMs Mohammed endorsed the comments by
OL,18,Fthe Archbishops of Canterbury and
OL,19,FYork, calling for a "comprehensive
OL,20,Fdialogue".
