OL,6,FShe said: "Since its inception, the
OL,7,FMuslim Council of Britain has
OL,8,Fchampioned the common good, urging its
OL,9,Faffiliates to make positive
OL,10,Fcontributions to our nation, foster
OL,11,Funity, and advocate for justice for
OL,12,Fall communities. These are the shared
OL,13,Fvalues of Britain, even if certain
OL,14,Fmembers of the Government fail to
OL,15,Frecognise them."
OL,17,FThursday's announcement comes against
OL,18,Fa background of rising antisemitic and
OL,19,FIslamophobic incidents since the
OL,20,FOctober 7 attacks in Israel.
