OL,6,FThe Community Security Trust, which
OL,7,Fprovides security for the Jewish
OL,8,Fcommunity, recorded a 147% increase in
OL,9,Fantisemitic incidents in 2023, while
OL,10,Fthe national project Tell Mama has
OL,11,Frecorded a 335% increase in anti-
OL,12,FMuslim hate cases in the last four
OL,13,Fmonths.
OL,15,FSeparately, a poll for the think tank
OL,16,FMore in Common found 25% of the public
OL,17,Fthought the UK was unsafe for Muslims
OL,18,Fand 35% thought it was unsafe for Jews.
