OL,6,FMr Gove added: "The pervasiveness of
OL,7,Fextremist ideologies has become
OL,8,Fincreasingly clear in the aftermath of
OL,9,Fthe October 7 attacks and poses a real
OL,10,Frisk to the security of our citizens
OL,11,Fand our democracy.
OL,13,F"This is the work of extreme right-
OL,14,Fwing and Islamist extremists who are
OL,15,Fseeking to separate Muslims from the
OL,16,Frest of society and create division
